      "updated": 1703000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "step = max(1, floor(timeline.length / 60))\nsampled to max 60 bars\n\nX: interaction step index\nY: predicted probability %\n50% ReferenceLine (gray dashed)\n\nBar fill per entry:\n  entry.correct (response===1) \u2192 #22c55e (green)\n  else                         \u2192 #ef4444 (red)\nfillOpacity: 0.8  \u00b7  maxBarSize: 8",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "step = max(1, floor(timeline.length / 60))\nsampled to max 60 bars\n\nX: interaction step index\nY: predicted probability %\n50% ReferenceLine (gray dashed)\n\nBar fill per entry:\n  entry.correct (response===1) \u2192 #22c55e (green)\n  else                         \u2192 #ef4444 (red)\nfillOpacity: 0.8  \u00b7  maxBarSize: 8",
