      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4-card grid:\n\nCritical   avgM < 0.3\n  red border/bg\n\nHigh Risk  0.3 \u2264 avgM < 0.5\n  amber border/bg\n\nModerate   0.5 \u2264 avgM < 0.75\n  blue border/bg\n\nProficient avgM >= 0.75\n  emerald border/bg\n\nCount = classStats.filter(tier).length\nsub: \"of N students\"",
