      "updated": 1703000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "cohortTrajectory: max 20 points\nstep = max(1,floor(refTl.length/20))\n\nLine 1 cohortAvg \u2014 \u2014 \u2014\n  gray dashed strokeWidth=2\n  class average across all students\nLine 2 studentMastery \u2014\u2014\u2014\n  #f97316 strokeWidth=2.5\n  current student\n\n75% proficiency reference\n  emerald dashed\nTooltip: class avg% \u00b7 student%\nHidden if allStudents.length < 2",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "cohortTrajectory: max 20 points\nstep = max(1,floor(refTl.length/20))\n\nLine 1 cohortAvg \u2014 \u2014 \u2014\n  gray dashed strokeWidth=2\n  class average across all students\nLine 2 studentMastery \u2014\u2014\u2014\n  #f97316 strokeWidth=2.5\n  current student\n\n75% proficiency reference\n  emerald dashed\nTooltip: class avg% \u00b7 student%\nHidden if allStudents.length < 2",
