      "text": "Sorted: avgM asc\n\nColumns:\n  Student (mono)\n  [Viewing] badge on current\n  Avg Mastery\n    <50% \u2192 red bold\n    \u226575% \u2192 emerald\n    mid  \u2192 blue\n  At-Risk Skills\n    >0 \u2192 destructive badge\n    0  \u2192 emerald text\n  Proficient above75/nSkills\n  Trend  \u2191 \u2192 \u2193\n\nonClick row \u2192 setSelectedUid(uid)",
