      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1703000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Filter:\n  avgM < 0.5 OR trend=down\n  max 8 students\n\nAmber bordered card\nper flagged student\n\nBadge by severity:\n  avgM < 0.3\n  \u2192 Schedule review session\n    (destructive)\n  trend = down\n  \u2192 Assign practice exercises\n    (default)\n  else\n  \u2192 Monitor closely\n\n\u2713 \"No students flagged\"\n  if all passing",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Filter:\n  avgM < 0.5 OR trend=down\n  max 8 students\n\nAmber bordered card\nper flagged student\n\nBadge by severity:\n  avgM < 0.3\n  \u2192 Schedule review session\n    (destructive)\n  trend = down\n  \u2192 Assign practice exercises\n    (default)\n  else\n  \u2192 Monitor closely\n\n\u2713 \"No students flagged\"\n  if all passing",
